[Customize Webconverger](http://webconverger.com/buy/) for your own homepage like banks, museums, car dealerships and many other customers have done. Most customers just need their [[homepage]] customised, however there are further options:

This page lists technical features. For non-technical argumentation see [the About Webconverger page.](http://webconverger.com/about/)

# [[mini]]

1. [[ISO]] (with [[grub|boot]]) and/or [[USB]] image varieties for [download](http://download.webconverger.com/)
* [Firefox Web browser](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Firefox) 2.x rebuild [Iceweasel](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iceweasel) by default in every Webconverger.
* Automatic update on bootup - Webconverger has an [[upgrade]] feature
* [[Artwork]] - your $HOMEPAGE/bg.png, default being [http://portal.webconverger.com/bg.png](http://portal.webconverger.com/bg.png).
* Kiosk reset with `kioskresetstation=<mins>`. Resets browser after user defined minutes of idleness/inactivity.
* [[Networking]] customisation. Default is wired DHCP.
* [[Adobe]] (Macromedia) Flash & [PDF viewing](http://flickr.com/photos/hendry/851173358/)

# [[maxi]] = [[mini]] + extras (mainly support for non-English locales)

* [[Extensive_internationalization_support|i18n]] -  Exotic locales such as Chinese, Japanese and Korean (CJK) are supported. CJK keyboard switching via [scim](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SCIM) and many other types of keyboard setups, such as Swiss German. Spelling support with dictionaries in many languages. [[maxi]] only.
* [[Printing]] support

